categories: Category:Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter voice actors

nodes.text: Charles Rocket (August 24, 1949–October 7, 2005) voiced the Feeorin Nym in Star Wars: Starfighter and Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter. He was credited as Charlie Rocket in both games.
Rocket was also known as the villain Nicholas Andre in the film Dumb & Dumber.
